high_descs: Walk to the blue bin to the right of the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap from the blue bin.
Turn around and walk to the tub.
Put the bar of soap to the right of the rag.
Move to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap to the left of the sink.
Walk back over to the tub.
Place the second bar of soap to the right of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the tub.

high_descs: Take a step to the right to face the trash can on the floor.
Pick up the soap in the trash can.
Turn around and walk forward to face the tub.
Place the soap in the middle of the bath tub.
Turn around and walk forward to face the vanity.
Pick up the soap on the left side of the vanity.
Turn around and walk forward to face the tub.
Place the soap in the middle of the bath tub next to the first soap.
anns.task_desc: To place two bars of soap in the middle of the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward a step, turn left, go forward to the blue bin.
Take the bar of soap from the bin.
Turn around, go forward to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the tub.
Turn right, go forward to the door, turn right, go forward to the counter to the left of the sink.
Take the bar of soap from the counter.
Turn right, go forward to the toilet, turn right, go forward to the tub.
Put the bar of soap in the tub to the right of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in a bath tub.
